At Damp Solving Water & Mold, we take great pride in providing fast, reliable, professional, and friendly service to our valued customers. We understand that dealing with water damage or mold can be a stressful and overwhelming experience, and we strive to alleviate your worries by offering compassionate and efficient solutions. Fundraisers of any size, from individuals raising money for a cause to school/community groups to large nonprofits, can set up a free fundraising page and select up to three deals at local and national brands. The fundraisers then uses tools available through GoodTwo as well as their own donor list to let potential donors know about the fundraiser. For every deal sold, half the profits that GoodTwo receives are given as a donation. (The donation for each deal is clearly spelled out in the buying process.) All fulfillment, customer service, deal negotiation, etc. is handled by GoodTwo. The fundraiser simply extends the offers to its database.
Industry Groups: Commerce and Shopping, Other, Social Impact

Emmy-winning correspondents. Leaders of finance and industry. National security experts. Podium Prose speakers bring prestige, expertise, and eloquence to your event.  Podium Prose writers have assisted scores of business executives, government leaders, political candidates and non-profit organizations communicate their ideas through crisp, memorable speeches and powerful written materials.  Speech writing is Podium Prose specialty. Podium Prose doesn't believe in and will never use, boilerplate prose. There is no one-size-fits-all solution when it comes to public speaking. Podium Prose tailors speeches to the style of the individual, the needs of the audience and the subject matter being addressed. Podium Prose job isn't finished until speech is a completely comfortable fit.  Beyond speech writing, Podium Prose has also produced op-ed pieces, website text, white papers, press releases, annual reports, video scripts, and an assortment of collateral materials.  Podium Prose trainers will provide tips on how to prepare to give a speech, how to deal with nervousness, and how to feel comfortable in front of an audience. For more experienced speakers, Podium Prose will analyze style and offer advice on how to bolster strengths and improve any vulnerabilities in how you address your audiences.  Podium Prose also works with executives and political figures on how to handle media interviews. This involves a variety of skills, from eye contact to body language to effectively summarizing message and following agenda, not interviewer's.
